trans-unit.source: Gives the process host an infinite lifetime by preventing a lease from being created.

trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> para indicar que se debe cargar previamente la aplicación; de lo contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Notifies ASP.NET that a particular application that is running on [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] is configured to be preloaded.
trans-unit.target: Notifica a ASP.NET que una aplicación determinada que se está ejecutando en [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] está configurada para cargarse previamente.

trans-unit.source: This method implements the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager.SetApplicationPreloadState%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager> interface.
trans-unit.target: Este método implementa el <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager.SetApplicationPreloadState%2A> método de la <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager> interfaz.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] calls the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager.SetApplicationPreloadState%2A> method to notify ASP.NET whether the application that is being loaded supports preloading.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] llamadas a la <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager.SetApplicationPreloadState%2A> método para notificar a ASP.NET si admite la precarga de la aplicación que se va a cargar.

trans-unit.source: This method applies only to applications that run on [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Este método solo se aplica a las aplicaciones que se ejecutan en [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="enabled" /> is set to <see langword="true" /> and the process host was not previously passed an <see cref="T:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil" /> interface to its <see cref="M:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager.SetApplicationPreloadUtil(System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil)" /> method
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="enabled" /> está establecido en <see langword="true" /> y el host del proceso no pasó una interfaz <see cref="T:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil" /> a su método <see cref="M:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager.SetApplicationPreloadUtil(System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil)" /> previamente

trans-unit.source: The handle to an unmanaged interface in [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] that ASP.NET calls to get information.
trans-unit.target: Controlador para una interfaz no administrada en [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] al que ASP.NET llama para obtener información.

trans-unit.source: Creates a type that calls [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] to get information that is required in order to preload an application.
trans-unit.target: Crea un tipo que llama a [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] para obtener información necesaria para cargar previamente una aplicación.

trans-unit.source: This method implements the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager.SetApplicationPreloadUtil%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager> interface.
trans-unit.target: Este método implementa el <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager.SetApplicationPreloadUtil%2A> método de la <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadManager> interfaz.

trans-unit.source: The method creates an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil> type, which calls into [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] to get preloading information.
trans-unit.target: El método crea una instancia de la <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil> tipo, que llama a [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] para obtener precargar información.

trans-unit.source: This method applies only to applications that run on [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Este método solo se aplica a las aplicaciones que se ejecutan en [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil" /> instance that contains information for preloading the application is not <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: La instancia <see cref="T:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil" /> que contiene información para cargar previamente la aplicación no es <see langword="null" />.
